  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this clinical study was to obtain type 1 diabetes data to identify models for
      glucose prediction and control and to construct a physiological
      pharmaco-kinetic/pharmaco-dynamic computer model of a type 1 diabetic person.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
