  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  diabetes duration &gt; 5 years

          -  HbA1c &lt; or = 7.2%

          -  CSII treated for &gt; 3 months

          -  Capable of being moderately, physically active for 20 minutes

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  symptoms of diabetic late complications except simplex retinopathy

          -  pregnancy or nursing
      </textblock>
